# Richard Ogazi — Portfolio Website

A clean, fast, and professional developer portfolio built with React, TypeScript, and Tailwind CSS.

🔗 **Live site:** [richardogazi.vercel.app](https://richiernieportfolio-hk1ve2uun-richieernies-projects.vercel.app/)

---

## Tech Stack

- **React 18** — component-based UI
- **TypeScript** — type-safe JavaScript
- **Tailwind CSS** — utility-first styling
- **Vite** — fast build tool and dev server
- **Lucide React** — icon library

---

## Sections

- Hero — introduction and code card
- About — background and stats
- Skills — frontend and tools
- Projects — CineRich, Shopmia, Expense Tracker, Smart Waste System
- Experience — my journey
- Contact — links and email

---

## Run Locally

```bash
git clone https://github.com/RichieErnie/Portfolio
cd richard-portfolio
npm install
npm run dev
```

Open [http://localhost:5173](http://localhost:5173)

---

## Deployment

Deployed on **Vercel**. Every push to `main` triggers an automatic redeploy.

